text: Please remove all "(PRD XXX)" references in the settings menus

proposedTasks.title: Remove PRD section references from settings UI
proposedTasks.description: Audit all settings menus and configuration screens and remove any visible '(PRD XXX)' references (e.g., '(PRD 6.5)', '(Section 5.9)'). These are internal document references meant for developers, not end users. Acceptance criteria: (1) No text matching the pattern '(PRD ...)', '(Section ...)', or '(...)' appears anywhere in user-facing settings UI, (2) Tooltips, labels, descriptions, and placeholder text in all settings panels are reviewed, (3) Replacement copy is plain, user-friendly language that describes the setting's purpose without citing the PRD.

taskTitles: Remove PRD section references from settings UI
